  "description": "A panoramic view captures a dramatic seascape dominated by a long bridge stretching across a wide body of water. The bridge, a suspension bridge with tall, slender towers, appears as a delicate line against the backdrop of the setting or rising sun, creating a warm golden glow. The water reflects the muted light, and distant landmasses are shrouded in a soft haze. A smaller, concrete causeway extends into the water, and numerous small boats dot the surface. Above, a thick layer of dark, moody clouds hangs low, adding to the dramatic atmosphere. The distant hills create a subtle horizon line.",
